Pagination
 
jquery.pagination.js
1. Accepts an options object to configure items per page (itemsPerPage) and the class name used on the navigation (navigationClass).

{
itemsPerPage: 7,
navigationClass: 'pagination'
}

pagination.css
1. Modify the Buttons/Arrows, size, and colors to be used for paginated navigation.
2. Modify styles for paginated list content.

pagination.html
1. Sample content of how files should be included, how list should be setup, and how to select where to include paginated navigation.

arrows folder
1. Contains images for arrow buttons.